{"tid":1361392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［遍地開花］大明王朝先帝告全港老百姓聖旨","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T01:49:53.000Z","uid":17641,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f738b9d6568eec0e2e5edc382ac748d64d696836","tid":1361392,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.gvm.com.tw/upload/gallery/20190425/60607_00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gvm.com.tw%2Fupload%2Fgallery%2F20190425%2F60607_00.jpg&h=0d89759b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奉天承運先帝 詔曰: 向我香江自大英失馭，匪共入而據之, 播胡俗以腥膻, 香江英姿不竟，匪非我類，入主香江廿二年，因特府失政，首倡禍亂，官黑勾結，污壞彝倫，綱常失序，為民巨害，孰不與憤，卿本香江之舊家，恥前王辱，興師振旅，掃蕩匪共，當此之時，天運循環，香江氣盛，百萬之中，奉天舉義，驅逐匪共，恢復香江，立綱陳紀，救濟斯民。<br />\n欽此<br />\n大明崇禎三百九十二年六月廿二<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0840ad49b967c1323dfff592f7916ad71cb37571","tid":1361392,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5f5762b7f3601f8daed4383a8923e5739bede10e","tid":1361392,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda1893f876406731d569e56e116cbf0da03c4fd","tid":1361392,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0d2e21072f37f941499f1ad88fc0883be4e50a","tid":1361392,"uid":1110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"先帝顯靈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmo